Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾經很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很想大哭一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論何時也不是孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.39,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遙遠的夢想在閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將它找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把雙眼閉上便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在心中的一個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算留下傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.88,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要害怕 現在是兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要放棄 Step by step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓著夢想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,經常也和你一起向明天邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,繼續前進 Step by step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想堅信著 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.71,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想向著天空大聲呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃燒著 in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.10,0:01:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫戰部渡,為了打倒支配著遙遠星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.30,0:01:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又再一次成為救世主,進行冒險旅程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.23,0:01:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星界山的第一星界是有趣的童話世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.81,0:01:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這裏我們要把令花盛開的星之風吹起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在加拉查鎮打倒了哈蒂娜的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向星之風宮殿的所在地超力布村出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.25,0:02:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.42,0:02:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第六話\N快點吹起吧,星之風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.35,0:02:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是星之風宮殿嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是個巨大的風車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.83,0:02:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的確,說是宮殿的話,叫做風車比較適合呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.86,0:02:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒是村內的人去了哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,格嘰,格嘰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.58,0:03:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你,只有這間屋… 這座風車求你放過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.63,0:03:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,格嘰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.44,0:03:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野牛武一郎流,電光交叉字斬!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飄飄攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.57,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我什麼也沒有做過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請問…你們是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.11,0:04:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看啊,渡 這裏有花開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼說,這條村有星之風在吹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.71,0:04:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是,星之風其實是由用這條村附近的特別樹木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所做的風車所吹起的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼令村中的風車轉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一星界的花就會複原了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.01,0:04:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,只是村裏的風車,是沒法恢複原狀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要令第一星界的花盛開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不令星之風宮殿的風車轉動是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.19,0:04:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本來這個超力布村是守護著星之風宮殿的村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.66,0:04:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宮殿的風車不每天上鏈就會停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.73,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天不斷為它上鏈是我們的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.81,0:05:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然出現的第一星界的波士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西把宮殿霸佔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他把我們上鏈的工作禁止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後星之風就停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.02,0:05:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一星界的花也消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過分,真是過分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不能饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們會打倒露易·瑪格西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對會令星之風再次吹起給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.32,0:05:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪了,這裏明明經常也有守衛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是下午茶時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.69,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.06,0:06:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之不打破這道門就進不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家幫我一把吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裏到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.73,0:06:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小渡,那裏是在下的背上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,紅紅一片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然好像是在宮殿裏面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等你很久了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.65,0:06:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的部下雖然絕對不是可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.23,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但也是忠心於我,但你竟然欺負他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.21,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.51,0:06:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"久等了,久等了" 嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.31,0:07:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是火美子,大叔是"久等了"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.45,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是"久等了" 是瑪格西,瑪格西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.56,0:07:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,露易·瑪格西,快把村中的風車複原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.20,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想令風車轉動就先要打倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.93,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣?要用決鬥方式決勝負嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,決鬥嗎?看來你不知道在下的實力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼武器當然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍嗎?要看看是否中獎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用這個決定決鬥的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.23,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是說,決鬥是用這個幸運輪魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在你喜歡的時候停下來就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸運輪轉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,首先由在下開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.11,0:07:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望會中頭獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,不是這個問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.79,0:08:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中大獎,恐怖的獨木橋蒙眼決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.49,0:08:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恐怖的獨木橋蒙眼決鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,掉下去就成為鱷魚點心的恐怖獨木橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,是河馬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然像,但那是鱷魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.32,0:08:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱷魚先生,你和河馬哪個較強啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,鱷魚先生很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.76,0:08:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開始了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.08,0:08:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.38,0:09:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油 加油,大叔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.95,0:09:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還沒夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的本領不錯呢,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.72,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒是你有興趣和星界山第一美女做朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星界山第一美女?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有破綻!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.72,0:09:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.81,0:09:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍法,河馬搖搖卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.72,0:09:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,這次到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.03,0:10:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中大獎,灼熱火海炎熱的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,怎麼辦?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.48,0:10:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了,現在可以用魚子神奇飯團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.61,0:10:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神奇飯團的魚子神奇飯團是用來防禦的飯團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.99,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃了後三分鐘內會有飯團開關的屏障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.96,0:10:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.33,0:10:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了,瑪格西!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.71,0:10:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要快點,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飯團只有三分鐘效力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.52,0:10:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三分鐘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼這三分鐘內我就慢慢和你玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.19,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.02,0:11:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪格西那家夥有心在拖延時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,已沒時間了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍部道具是超方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.16,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是雨珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雨珠?那這個怎樣用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熱的時候就用雨珠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火焰消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是誰在阻礙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.69,0:12:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我啊,這次和我決鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸運輪轉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.37,0:12:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?一號?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.49,0:12:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,決鬥方法是猜拳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猜拳,猜拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍法,望向那邊之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個樣子是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.09,0:12:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔,和我玩 "望向那邊"吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"望向那邊"也好,什麼都好 開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了,猜拳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.07,0:12:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.46,0:12:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我勝了,望向那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再來決鬥一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猜拳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又是我勝了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實我是剪刀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,望向那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.46,0:13:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,望向那邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了,火美子 做得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.50,0:13:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是"望向那邊"的冠軍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡,你這群小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已不能饒恕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把我的決鬥當作笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.84,0:13:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話,決鬥什麼已沒關係了 死吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.98,0:13:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們還是合力對付他比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.80,0:13:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逃吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和我堂堂正正決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,要跑到哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那邊是出口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.53,0:13:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了一個很糟的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.04,0:14:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦,現在又不能回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.12,0:14:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之衝過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.45,0:14:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.45,0:14:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,那個姐姐交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這我早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.06,0:14:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實…我最怕高的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛剛獨木橋的時候 不是好好的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒看到反而就很放心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.00,0:14:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再磨磨蹭蹭的會被瑪格西抓到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣也沒關係嗎?餵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡…我的腰動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.79,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已逃不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪格西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.93,0:14:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想知道用來替宮殿的風車上鏈的鑽子在哪裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就當是送你到地獄的送別禮,告訴你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鑽子就在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟在那地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.71,0:15:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,差不多是時候解決你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.82,0:15:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是機會了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.58,0:15:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飄飄攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.73,0:15:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.26,0:15:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,我一會兒也會來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.07,0:15:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次是打算用魔神襲擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇一跳的事現在才開始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧,黑暗馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.83,0:16:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我絕不會把風車的鑽子,交給你們的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.71,0:16:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯?我好像聽見什麼奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.71,0:16:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋,渡,竟躲在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.77,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧,先收拾你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.21,0:16:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧,蠍子連珠炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.54,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太卑鄙了,瑪格西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.55,0:16:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.90,0:16:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛吧,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.24,0:17:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,剛才決鬥的勝負在這裏分吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.30,0:17:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼決鬥啊?又再想用卑鄙方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.27,0:17:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍雷拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度真快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因為那家夥坐著的馬的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能夠追上黑暗馬的速度嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.00,0:18:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他來了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.20,0:18:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧,蠍子攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勝負已分了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.85,0:18:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.94,0:18:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不打倒他,第一星界就不能恢複原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像想做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.87,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,就這樣把他撞去地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是時候了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.68,0:19:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.60,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.27,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.04,0:19:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最討厭輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是風車的鑽子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?那部魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道,我也沒見過這魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,鑽子啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,風車開始轉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轉了轉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們看,是星之風啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.31,0:21:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來第一星界已恢複原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.31,0:21:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,旅程還只是剛剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要放鬆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,這次是第二星界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.80,0:22:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?這個胸口在驅跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.47,0:22:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop!已不能停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.36,0:22:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連你也一個勁兒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.21,0:22:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,油門不用放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.46,0:22:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直踏著 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.58,0:22:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.62,0:23:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為是速度的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,TONIGHT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.56,0:23:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.61,0:23:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能夠抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直望著的瞳孔湧上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.93,0:23:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.15,0:23:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今夜 MY LOVE
